{"talk":{"id":26915,"name":"Dolly Chugh: How to let go of being a \"good\" person -- and become a better person","description":"What if your attachment to being a \"good\" person is holding you back from actually becoming a better person? In this accessible talk, social psychologist Dolly Chugh explains the puzzling psychology of ethical behavior -- like why it's hard to spot your biases and acknowledge mistakes -- and shows how the path to becoming better starts with owning your mistakes. \"In every other part of our lives, we give ourselves room to grow -- except in this one, where it matters most,\" Chugh says.","slug":"dolly_chugh_how_to_let_go_of_being_a_good_person_and_become_a_better_person","recorded_at":"2018-10-03 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-11-01 14:46:09","updated_at":"2021-04-13 21:28:42","viewed_count":2831175,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":562,"name":"TED@BCG Toronto"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/24147a1e6b5a9acd2e3e1d8b95c9d4c354cd44a6_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/24147a1e6b5a9acd2e3e1d8b95c9d4c354cd44a6_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/24147a1e6b5a9acd2e3e1d8b95c9d4c354cd44a6_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/24147a1e6b5a9acd2e3e1d8b95c9d4c354cd44a6_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/89610c1e62d706d471d2839b5a4033185ac8c621_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DollyChugh_2018S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5827462,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DollyChugh_2018S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":16155381,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DollyChugh_2018S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7daf